# label: TOOL
# role: hunt for COMPLEX beginner.py successes (≥N compound moves)

Variant of `one_card_hunt.py` / `beginner_hunt.py` that
filters for stuck states `beginner.py` resolves with deeper
plans (compound-move count above a threshold). Used during
corpus assembly to capture the harder Steve-level puzzles.

